cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD 

This paper deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis, which are core topics in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of discourse relations to propagate affective polarity is a machine learning technique, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of raw corpora and small seed lexicons, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and software development (cs.SD).
